      "full_name": "OJSC “Machine-building plant ‘Mayak’”",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "OJSC “Machine-building plant ‘Mayak’” is a Russian military industry company delivering components to the other military plants producing military airplanes for the Russian Ministry of Defence. OJSC “Mayak” is part of the Aviation Equipment Holding. The Aviation Equipment Holding is one of 14 integrated structures that are part of the Rostec State Corporation. OJSC “Mayak” manufactures electrical units and instruments for the Russian Army fighter jets, fighter-bombers and attack helicopters, including Su-25, Su-27, Su-30, MiG-31, Mi-28 and Ka-50/52, that are being operated during Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}